metadata.title: ExpressItBest Aluminum Dog Tag Necklace and Key Ring - Flag of Colombia (Colombian) - Rustic/USA
features: Vibrant, high-grade aluminum dog tag with glossy finish
Measures 2" x 1.125" (5cm x 3cm) and can be worn as a necklace or used as a keychain
Includes both a key ring and a 30" (76cm) chain with clasp closure
Same image printed on both sides for maximum visual impact
Makes a thoughtful gift for any occasion. Proudly imprinted in the U.S.A. in our facility.
description: Looking for a unique way to express yourself or a thoughtful gift for a friend? Look no further than our vibrantly printed dog tags! Made from high-grade aluminum with a glossy finish, these tags feature the same image on both sides for maximum visual impact. Measuring 2" x 1.125" (5cm x 3cm), these tags can be worn as a necklace or used as a keychain, and come with both a key ring and a 30" (76cm) chain with a clasp closure. And with each tag imprinted in the U.S.A., these make a great gift for any occasion.
